OL,3,CPensioners 'have been biggest winners
OL,4,Cfrom tax and benefit changes since
OL,5,C2010'
OL,7,FThe triple lock, which is used to
OL,8,Fincrease state pensions annually, is a
OL,9,Fdriver behind the improvements for
OL,10,Fpensioners.
OL,12,FIt has led to the state pension
OL,13,Fgrowing by 60% between 2010-11 and
OL,14,F2023-24, faster than the 46% growth in
OL,15,Faverage earnings, the report said.
OL,17,FDemographic pressures and policies
OL,18,Fhave shifted the balance of state
OL,19,Fspending towards pensioners since
OL,20,F2010, researchers found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
