OL,7,FSpending on pensioners has grown from
OL,8,F9.3% of GDP in 2009-10 to 9.8% in 2024-
OL,9,F25, according to the research, funded
OL,10,Fby the Nuffield Foundation.
OL,12,FBut while benefit policies have
OL,13,Fgenerally made pensioners better off,
OL,14,Ftax changes, such as the recent cuts
OL,15,Fto employee national insurance, have
OL,16,Fhelped to rebalance the "winners" and
OL,17,F"losers", the report said.
