OL,7,FLooking at all permanent tax and
OL,8,Fbenefit changes since 2010, the
OL,9,Fresearch found that pensioner
OL,10,Fhouseholds are #1,000 a year better
OL,11,Foff on average in 2024-25, while
OL,12,Fworking-age households are #760 a year
OL,13,Fbetter off.
OL,15,FHowever, some groups have been left
OL,16,Fworse off, according to the foundation.
