OL,7,FFor example, households with children
OL,8,Faged 14 and under are typically #780 a
OL,9,Fyear worse off in 2024-25, as any tax
OL,10,Fgains have been more than offset by
OL,11,Fcuts to many child-related benefits,
OL,12,Fthe report said.
OL,14,FThe foundation argued that the main
OL,15,Ftask facing Britain is to restart the
OL,16,Fgenerational progress on living
OL,17,Fstandards.
