OL,7,FPeople born in the late 1980s earned
OL,8,Fon average 8% less at age 30 than
OL,9,Fpeople born 10 years earlier did at
OL,10,Fthe same age, it said.
OL,12,FStronger economic growth will hold the
OL,13,Fkey to restarting this progress,
OL,14,Frather than specific policies targeted
OL,15,Fat different age cohorts, according to
OL,16,Fthe foundation, which is focused on
OL,17,Fimproving the living standards for
OL,18,Fthose on low to middle incomes.
