OL,7,FShe said that while both the
OL,8,FConservatives and Labour have a wide
OL,9,Frange of policies targeted at specific
OL,10,Fage cohorts "ultimately these policies
OL,11,Fwon't decide whether the new
OL,12,Fgeneration of young adults enjoys
OL,13,Fhigher living standards than their
OL,14,Fpredecessors".
OL,16,F"That will only come from stronger
OL,17,Feconomic growth," she added.
